rows.label: tlk70000044_02_msg0001
rows.name:
Morimori quite hungry right
now, but not eating very much.

rows.label: tlk70000044_02_msg0002
rows.name:
So many sad and frightened people
around that appetite is gone.
Food taste like cardboard.

rows.label: tlk70000044_02_msg0003
rows.name:
Morimori love food, but
even more love Iira and
chirpy-happy people of Iira.

rows.label: tlk70000044_02_msg0004
rows.name:
Maybe one day Iira go back to
being city where people can
eat and be merry again...
